price: 92.Yalli isi ginók qellittam kee tambulleem inkih yaaxigi kinni, tokkel Yalli agleh kaat hayya haanamak fayya iyyeeh, saytunnooweh.
arabic: عَٰلِمِ ٱلۡغَيۡبِ وَٱلشَّهَٰدَةِ فَتَعَٰلَىٰ عَمَّا يُشۡرِكُونَ

version.title: Afar translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Afar by a group of scholars. under supervision of Shaikh Mahmud Abdulkader Hamza. 1441 H.
